{"tid":2517201,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"4人荃灣暴動罪成 練錦鴻判監4年3個月至4年8個月","createTime":"2021-05-05T07:34:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T07:54:25.000Z","uid":240362,"like":8,"dislike":47,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"473bc5d2034078d22bd62b6460fbd687a44da66d","tid":2517201,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:34:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15468\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F15468&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mnwbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=74d96194\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15468</a><br />\n<br />\n#區域法院第七庭<br />\n#練錦鴻法官 🔥 #判刑<br />\n#1001荃灣 #暴動<br />\nD1陳(40), D2陳(20)<br />\nD3李(26), D5郭(23)<br />\n🛑四位已還押20日🛑<br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n1) 暴動 [各被告]<br />\n各被告同被控於2019年10月1日在香港新界荃灣海壩街，與其他身份不詳的人參與暴動。 <br />\n<br />\n2) 縱火 [D1]<br />\nD1被控於同日同地與其他不知名人士，無合理辯解下用火損壞另一人的財物。 <br />\n<br />\n--------------------------<br />\n🛑各被告於上次裁決被練錦鴻法官判處所面對的控罪全部罪名成立 (<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15048\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F15048&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mnwbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=39d396f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15048</a>)。<br />\n--------------------------<br />\n今早求情陳詞 (<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15452\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F15452&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mnwbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=47dd78bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15452</a>)<br />\n--------------------------<br />\n<br />\n判刑速報‼️：<br />\nD1:<br />\n控罪(1): 量刑起點為4年6個月<br />\n控罪(2): 量刑起點為4年6個月<br />\n2個月分期執行，總刑期為4年8個月‼️<br />\n<br />\nD2:<br />\n控罪(1): 量刑起點為4年6個月，求情+沒有嚴重挑戰案情扣減3個月，判處即時監禁4年3個月‼️<br />\n<br />\nD3:<br />\n控罪(1): 量刑起點為4年6個月，求情+沒有嚴重挑戰案情扣減3個月，判處即時監禁4年3個月‼️<br />\n<br />\nD5:<br />\n控罪(1): 量刑起點為4年6個月，求情扣減1個月，判處即時監禁4年5個月‼️"},{"pid":"676e86b5eb0b9b9d0fd115c5ea51a969d712e4d9","tid":2517201,"uid":159271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:36:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\ncls"},{"pid":"283b408374a75dda171772dad2ab69d77a38aa86","tid":2517201,"uid":289946,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:36:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7671152bc9b7ad30e070b9fe83315576cf947d9e","tid":2517201,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:37:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f62fb6dafc73eaa856a6d30cfa6a5392c7cf7514","tid":2517201,"uid":171107,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:37:44.000Z","msg":"愈判愈重"},{"pid":"7113e2b213b542047a75748912d9c149d87a84dc","tid":2517201,"uid":76804,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:37:55.000Z","msg":"咁就四年<br />\n呢d出返黎之後真係要幫"},{"pid":"d116697fa5ca4c60e2d667f3a820a1599b6bfbfc","tid":2517201,"uid":76804,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"f62fb6dafc73eaa856a6d30cfa6a5392c7cf7514","tid":2517201,"uid":171107,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:37:44.000Z","msg":"愈判愈重"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:38:27.000Z","msg":"暴動不嬲都係4年起跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf0f49867512b092ce94eecd