0月1日在荃灣遭警員射實彈槍傷，連同另外6人被拘控暴動罪，其中3男1女早前在區域法院經審訊後被裁定暴動及縱火等罪名成立，還柙至今天判刑。辯方求情指被告於案中並無實質傷害警員，惟法官練錦鴻質疑被告在行人路上縱火，是否有意圖傷人；辯方則稱被告只為阻礙警方推進。最終四人分別被判監4年3個月至4年8個月。<br />\n<br />\n各人今晨應訊表現精神，李及郭在犯人欄內不時帶笑望向公眾席，李並隔着犯人欄與法律代表交談，其間有講有笑，又向聲援親友點頭。<br />\n<br />\n今天律師席上可見人權律師關尚義（John Clancey）的身影。他曾因涉嫌參與民主派初選、被指違反國安法被捕。據了解，他是本案其中一名被告的事務律師，協助向大狀作出指示。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210505/KE7SBOYJ7VCCROXZ4UKC72WRU4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210505%2FKE7SBOYJ7VCCROXZ4UKC72WRU4%2F&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mnwbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=e1f5e759\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210505%2FKE7SBOYJ7VCCROXZ4UKC72WRU4%2F&h=9226d091\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210505/KE7SBOYJ7VCCROXZ4UKC72WRU4/</a>"},{"pid":"53d4dd4f7f0db02106384c9373637c8c807dc29a","tid":2517201,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:49:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56cc00ab091c7da2626294e134df411d96160c91","tid":2517201,"uid":295650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66a6b5829539a788f43826509a5a22dee8cf32bd","tid":2517201,"uid":146351,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7113e2b213b542047a75748912d9c149d87a84dc","tid":2517201,"uid":76804,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:37:55.000Z","msg":"咁就四年<br />\n呢d出返黎之後真係要幫"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:46:04.000Z","msg":"坦白講 4年後仲有邊個記得佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:49:28.000Z","msg":"要搵到佢地先...."},{"pid":"72ada572e08bd1328e72559f0a18999f824abd54","tid":2517201,"uid":15697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6126350cf07416fdd07c558a3e11cbae1fc24e52","tid":2517201,"uid":125731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:42:28.000Z","msg":"個博士生呢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:49:50.000Z","m